Invocation Name: trump facts
des:
Ask for Trump Facts, and learn about the leader of the free world, as of October 2020.

Trump Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to teach you something new.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Trump Facts" or "Alexa, open Trump Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
